    • isCommentStyleKey

      public static boolean isCommentStyleKey(String key)
      Checks if a keywords is known to be a comment-style keyword. That is, it checks if the key argument matches any IFitsHeader constructed via this implementation with a valueType argument that was null, or if the key is empty.
      Parameters:
      key - the keyword to check
      Returns:
      true if the key is empty or if it matches any known IFitsHeader keywords implemented through this class that have valueType of null. Otherwise false.
      Since:
      1.17
